,"title":"Small Omega","text":"","tags":["numerical-analysis","notation"]},{"location":"blog/drafts/b-l_notations/#big-omega","title":"Big Omega","text":"","tags":["numerical-analysis","notation"]},{"location":"blog/drafts/b-l_notations/#_2","title":"\ucc38\uace0","text":"<ol> <li>Big O notation - Wikipedia</li> </ol>","tags":["numerical-analysis","notation"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/22/hom-set%EC%9D%B4-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%AB%ED%98%80%EC%9E%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4/","title":"hom-set\uc774 \uc5f0\uc0b0\uc5d0 \ub2eb\ud600\uc788\uc744 \uc870\uac74","text":"","tags":["category-theory","universal-algebra"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/22/hom-set%EC%9D%B4-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%AB%ED%98%80%EC%9E%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4/#_1","title":"\uad00\ucc30","text":"<p>magma \\({ X,Y }\\)\uac00 \uc8fc\uc6cc\uc84c\uc744 \ub54c morphism \\({ f,g:X \\to Y }\\)\uc5d0 \ub300\ud574\uc11c</p> \\[ (fg)(x_{1}x_{2})=f(x_{1}x_{2})g(x_{1}x_{2})=f(x_{1})f(x_{2})g(x_{1})g(x_{2}) \\] <p>\uc774\uace0</p> \\[ (fg)(x_{1})(fg)(x_{2})=f(x_{1})g(x_{1})f(x_{2})g(x_{2}) \\] <p>\uc774\ubbc0\ub85c \\({ fg }\\)\uac00 morphism\uc774\ub824\uba74 \uc784\uc758\uc758 \\({ x_{1}, x_{2} \\in X}\\)\uc5d0 \ub300\ud574 \ub2e4\uc74c \ub4f1\uc2dd\uc744 \ub9cc\uc871\ud574\uc57c \ud55c\ub2e4.</p> \\[ f(x_{1})f(x_{2})g(x_{1})g(x_{2})=f(x_{1})g(x_{1})f(x_{2})g(x_{2}) \\] <p>\uc704 \uad00\uacc4\uc2dd</p> \\[ (ab)(cd)=(ac)(bd) \\] <p>\ub97c mediality \ud639\uc740 entropicity\ub77c\uace0 \ubd80\ub978\ub2e4. \ub530\ub77c\uc11c \\({ \\text{Hom}(X,Y) }\\)\uac00 \\({ Y }\\)\uc758 \uc5f0\uc0b0\uc5d0\uc11c \uc720\ub3c4\ub41c \uc5f0\uc0b0\uc5d0 \ub2eb\ud600\uc788\uc744 \ucda9\ubd84\uc870\uac74\uc740 \\({ Y }\\)\uac00 medial magma\uc778 \uac83\uc774\ub2e4.</p>","tags":["category-theory","universal-algebra"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/22/hom-set%EC%9D%B4-%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0%EC%97%90-%EB%8B%AB%ED%98%80%EC%9E%88%EC%9D%84-%EC%A1%B0%EA%B1%B4/#_2","title":"\ucc38\uace0","text":"<ol> <li>Why is \\(\\operatorname{Hom}(A, B)\\) an abelian group? - Mathematics Stack Exchange</li> <li>Medial magma - Wikipedia</li> </ol>","tags":["category-theory","universal-algebra"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/29/%EB%9D%BC%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%91%EC%A3%BC-%EC%8A%B9%EC%88%98%EB%B2%95/","title":"\ub77c\uadf8\ub791\uc8fc \uc2b9\uc218\ubc95","text":"","tags":["optimization","calculus"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/29/%EB%9D%BC%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%91%EC%A3%BC-%EC%8A%B9%EC%88%98%EB%B2%95/#_2","title":"\ubc1c\uacac\uc801 \uc124\uba85","text":"<p>\\({ f,g: X \\subseteq \\mathbb{R}^{n} \\to \\mathbb{R} }\\) \uc774\uace0 \\({ S = \\left\\{x: g(x) = 0 \\right\\} }\\)\uc774\uba70 \\({ 0 }\\)\uc774 \\({ g }\\)\uc758 \uc815\uce59\uc810\uc774\ub77c\uace0 \ud558\uc790, \uadf8\ub7ec\uba74 \\({ f }\\)\uc758 \\({ S }\\) \uc704\uc758 \uc81c\ud55c \\({ \\left. f \\right\\rvert_{S} }\\)\uc758 \uadf9\uac12\uc744 \ucc3e\uc73c\ub824\uba74 \uc5b4\ub5bb\uac8c \ud574\uc57c\ud560\uae4c?</p> <p>\uc815\uce59\uace1\uc120 \\({ \\alpha : (-\\epsilon,\\epsilon) \\to S }\\)\uc5d0 \ub300\ud574\uc11c,</p> \\[ \\left. \\frac{d}{dt} \\right\\vert_{t=0} f(\\alpha(t)) = \\nabla f(\\alpha(0)) \\cdot \\alpha'(0)\\] <p>\ub530\ub77c\uc11c \\({ \\left. f \\right\\rvert_{S} }\\)\uac00 \\({ x \\in S }\\)\uc5d0\uc11c \uadf9\uac12\uc744 \uac00\uc9c0\uba74 \\({ x }\\)\uc5d0\uc11c \uc811\ud558\ub294 \\({ S }\\)\uc758 \uc811\ubca1\ud130 \\({ v }\\)\uc5d0 \ub300\ud574,</p> \\[ \\nabla f (x) \\cdot v = 0  \\] <p>\ud55c\ud3b8,</p> \\[ g(\\alpha(t)) = c \\implies \\left. \\frac{d}{dt} \\right\\rvert_{t=0} g(\\alpha(t)) = \\nabla g(\\alpha(0)) \\cdot \\alpha'(0) = 0 \\] <p>\ub530\ub77c\uc11c \\({ \\nabla g }\\)\ub294 \\({ S }\\)\uc758 \uc784\uc758\uc758 \uc811\ubca1\ud130 \\({ v }\\)\uc640 \uc9c1\uad50\ud55c\ub2e4. \uc989, \\({ \\nabla f }\\)\uc640 \\({ \\nabla g }\\)\uac00 \ud3c9\ud589\ud55c\ub2e4\ub294 \uac83\uc774\uace0 \uc801\ub2f9\ud55c \uc2e4\uc218 \\({ \\lambda \\neq 0 }\\)\uc774 \uc874\uc7ac\ud574,</p> \\[ \\nabla f = \\lambda \\nabla g \\] <p>\uc774\ub54c \\({ \\lambda }\\)\ub97c \ub77c\uadf8\ub791\uc8fc \uc2b9\uc218\ub77c\uace0 \ubd80\ub978\ub2e4.</p> <p>\uc815\ub9ac\ud558\uc790\uba74 \\({ \\left. f \\right\\rvert_{S} }\\)\uc758 \uadf9\uac12\uc744 \ucc3e\ub294 \uac83\uc740 \ub2e4\uc74c \uc5f0\ub9bd\ubc29\uc815\uc2dd\uc744 \ud478\ub294 \uac83\uacfc \uac19\ub2e4.</p> \\[ \\begin{dcases} g(x) = 0 &amp; \\text{(constraint euqation)} \\\\ \\nabla f(x) - \\lambda \\nabla g(x) = 0 &amp; \\text{(critical equation)} \\end{dcases} \\]","tags":["optimization","calculus"]},{"location":"blog/2025/06/29/%EB%9D%BC%EA%B7%B8%EB%9E%91%EC%A3%BC-%EC%8A%B9%EC%88%98%EB%B2%95/#_3","title":"\ub77c\uadf8\ub791\uc9c0\uc5b8 \ud568\uc218","text":"<p>\uc8fc\uc5b4\uc9c4 \ub450 \ud568\uc218 \\({ f,g : X \\subseteq \\mathbb{R}^{n} \\to \\mathbb{R} }\\)\uc5d0 \ub300\ud574, \ub77c\uadf8\ub791\uc9c0\uc5b8 \\({ L : X \\times \\mathbb{R} \\to \\mathbb{R} }\\)\ub97c \ub2e4\uc74c\uacfc \uac19\uc774 \uc815\uc758\ud574\ubcf4\uc790</p> \\[ L(x,\\lambda) = f(x) -\\lambda g(x) \\] <p>\uadf8\ub7ec\uba74,</p> \\[ L'(x,\\lambda) = \\left(\\nabla f(x) - \\lambda \\nabla g(x),\\, -g(x)\\right) \\] <p>\ub530\ub77c\uc11c \ubc29\uc815\uc2dd</p> \\[ L'(x,\\lambda) = (0,0) \\] <p>\uc740 \ub77c\uadf8\ub791\uc8fc \uc2b9\uc218\ubc95\uacfc \ub3d9\ub4f1\ud558\ub2e4.</p>","tags":["optimization","calculus"]},{"location":"blog/archive/2025/","title":"2025","text":""},{"location":"blog/category/%EC%88%98%ED%95%99/","title":"\uc218\ud559","text":""}]}